@startuml
|Authorized Staff|
start
:Open inventory transfer screen;
:Select source and destination location;
:Input variants and quantities;
:Submit transfer request;

|SESHOP System|
:Validate permission and quantity;
if (Permission valid?) then (yes)
  if (Enough stock at source?) then (yes)
    :Create transfer with status PENDING_APPROVAL;
    :Write audit log;

    |Super Admin|
    :Review transfer request;
    if (Approve transfer?) then (yes)
      |SESHOP System|
      :Mark transfer as APPROVED;
      :Deduct on-hand qty at source;
      :Increase in-transit qty;
      :Notify destination location;
      :When destination confirms receipt;
      :Increase on-hand qty at destination;
      :Complete transfer;
      :Write audit log;
    else (no)
      |SESHOP System|
      :Mark transfer as REJECTED;
      :Notify requester;
    endif
  else (no)
    :Reject request with insufficient stock message;
  endif
else (no)
  :Reject with unauthorized message;
endif
stop
@enduml
